node.text: 90 years after the Reverso was born, Jaeger-LeCoultre celebrates its watchmaking icon by releasing the most complicated timepiece ever presented in this emblematic collection. Discover the secrets of the world’s first watch with four sides premiering at Watches and Wonders Geneva 2021: the new Reverso Hybris Mechanica Calibre 185.

From the cosmos to your wrist.
#Reverso
_
Reverso Hybris Mechanica Calibre 185
_
By capitalizing for the very first time, on its three unique expertise of Precision, Sound and Celestial complications, to always go a step further. A total of eleven complications featuring a perpetual calendar, a flying tourbillon, a minute repeater and the most advanced lunar displays.
_

Spacetime, a perceptual art installation by Michael Murphy.
#ReversoStories
_
The Reverso Exhibition Shanghai, China.
Friend of the Maison Ni Ni @captainmiao
_
Spacetime is a captivating 3D rendition of the Reverso Tribute Nonantième, deepening the relationship between watchmaking and art. “My Reverso design explodes into an array of parts that tell a story about the watch and how it works.” – Michael Murphy. An original artwork presented at the Reverso Exhibition Shanghai, visited by Friend of the Maison Ni Ni @captainmiao on the opening night.
_

Reverso, a Story of Innovation.
#ReversoStories
_
The Reverso Exhibition Shanghai, China.
_
A Story of Innovation explores how the Reverso embodies Jaeger-LeCoultre’s eternally inventive quest for technical advancement. Beginning with the revolutionary idea of a case that could be flipped over, to the ingenious design by Rene-Alfred Chauvot, patented in 1931, the story traces the introduction of high-watchmaking complications.
_

Precision and elegance.
#JLCPolaris 
_
Polaris Chronograph
_
Equipped with a Jaeger-LeCoultre in-house mechanical movement featuring a column-wheel chronograph with a vertical clutch, the Polaris Chronograph is imbued with robustness and sporty elegance. Exuding refinement and adventure.
_

node.text:
The voice of memory.
#JLCPolaris 
_
Polaris Mariner Memovox
Friend of the Maison Benedict Cumberbatch
_
A story of time and precision. “It takes time and precision to make a few seconds worth of film, just like it takes time to make a watch. There is artistry in both, there’s also a large amount of technical ability.” – Friend of the Maison Benedict Cumberbatch, sporting the Polaris Mariner Memovox. 
_
#JaegerLeCoultre #BenedictCumberbatch #HomeofFineWatchmaking #JLCPolaris #Memovox #Watchmaking #SavoirFaire #Craftsmanship #SwissWatch

node.text:
Excellence in the details.
#JLCPolaris 
_
Polaris Mariner Date
_
An orange ring visible only when the crown at 2 o'clock is not screwed in, reminding the wearer that they have not adjusted the rehaut, leaving it free to any risky manipulation. Set the time, take a deep breath and immerse yourself in the blue depths.
_
#JaegerLeCoultre #HomeofFineWatchmaking #JLCPolaris #Watchmaking #SavoirFaire #Craftsmanship #SwissWatch

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Jaeger-LeCoultre on July 18, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text:
Pushing the limits further.
#JLCPolaris 
_
Polaris Mariner Date
_
Featuring a dual-crown configuration typical of super compressor-type watch cases, with the upper crown for operating the inner bezel and the lower one for setting the time and date. An instant-jumping date display complements outstanding watchmaking features.
_
#JaegerLeCoultre #HomeofFineWatchmaking #JLCPolaris #Watchmaking #SavoirFaire #Craftsmanship #SwissWatch

node.text:
42mm sports dial.
#JLCPolaris 
_
Polaris Mariner Date
_
In graduated shades of intense blue enhanced by a brilliant lacquer, a 42mm face that catches and captivates the eye. In bright, vivid white, the numerals and hour-markers exude an assertive look, standing out against the dial. 
_
#JaegerLeCoultre #HomeofFineWatchmaking #JLCPolaris #Watchmaking #SavoirFaire #Craftsmanship #SwissWatch

node.text:
From technical expertise to sophistication.
#JLCPolaris 
_
Polaris Mariner Memovox
Friend of the Maison Benedict Cumberbatch
_
“Jaeger-LeCoultre represents style, sophistication and technique. The manufacturing is exquisite, the engineering is “sans pareil”, the number of patents that the ateliers have amassed is extraordinary. Combined with what you see on your wrist, it’s a beautiful thing.” – Friend of the Maison Benedict Cumberbatch, wearing the Polaris Mariner Memovox.
_
#JaegerLeCoultre #BenedictCumberbatch #HomeofFineWatchmaking #JLCPolaris #Memovox #Watchmaking #SavoirFaire #Craftsmanship #SwissWatch
